ðŸ§­ Quick decision guide

I want internal microservice-to-microservice access â†’ ClusterIP Service
I want external access in Minikube quickly â†’ NodePort Service or minikube service myapp-nodeport
I want to test from my laptop without creating a Service â†’ port-forward
I need a URL with paths/TLS â†’ Ingress (plus a ClusterIP Service)


